== 發行 ==
《樂高旋風忍者電影》被[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]定於2017年9月22日在美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Batman Lego Movie, ‘Lego’ Sequel Get Release Dates|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/lego-movie-sequel-release-date-batman-ninjago-1201475916/|accessdate=2016-06-28|work=Variety|date=2015-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160619001330/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/lego-movie-sequel-release-date-batman-ninjago-1201475916/|archive-date=2016-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原本電影定於2016年9月23日推出<ref>{{cite news|title=“Ninjago” Coming to Theaters on September 23, 2016|url=http://www.warnerbros.com/studio/news/ninjago-coming-theaters-september-23-2016|accessdate=2016-06-28|work=Warner Bros|date=2014-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815165855/http://www.warnerbros.com/studio/news/ninjago-coming-theaters-september-23-2016|archive-date=2016-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年9月23日，電影的宣傳短片《''The Master''》於《[[送子鳥_(電影)|送子鳥]]》放映前推出<ref name="THRTheMaster">{{cite news|last1=Giardina|first1=Carolyn|title=New Lego Short 'The Master' to Debut Before 'Storks'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/new-lego-short-master-debut-922834|accessdate=2016-08-27|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826195809/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/new-lego-short-master-debut-922834|archive-date=2016-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
《樂高旋風忍者電影》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據131條評論，該片持有55%的新鮮度，平均得分為5.83／10<ref>{{cite web|title=''The Lego Ninjago Movie'' (2017)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lego_ninjago_movie|accessdate=2017-09-22|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921225238/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_lego_ninjago_movie|archive-date=2017-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上則獲得了55分，這代表「好壞平均參雜的評價」<ref>{{cite web|title=''The Lego Ninjago Movie'' reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-lego-ninjago-movie|accessdate=2017-09-22|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922003345/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-lego-ninjago-movie|archive-date=2017-09-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]的調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="opening">{{cite web|title='Kingsman: The Golden Circle’ Ropes $38M+; ‘Ninjago’ Dulls Sword To $21M; ‘Friend Request’ A Loner With $1.8M|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/kingsman-the-golden-circle-friend-request-lego-ninjago-box-office-weekend-1202174929/|accessdate=2017-09-23|date=2017-09-23|last=D'Allesandro|first=Anthony|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170922201001/http://deadline.com/2017/09/kingsman-the-golden-circle-friend-request-lego-ninjago-box-office-weekend-1202174929/|archive-date=2017-09-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國，《樂高旋風忍者電影》與《[[金牌特務：機密對決|金牌特務：機密對決]]》、《[[非死不可|非死不可]]》同週上映並競爭，分析師估計《樂高旋風忍者電影》於首映週末能從4070間戲院中獲得2700萬至4400萬美元的票房<ref>{{Cite web|title='Kingsman: The Golden Circle' and 'Lego Ninjago' will battle 'It' for box office victory|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-it-kingsman-lego-ninjago-20170920-htmlstory.html|accessdate=2017-09-20|date=2017-09-20|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920135717/http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-it-kingsman-lego-ninjago-20170920-htmlstory.html|archive-date=2017-09-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=September B.O. Booming To Near All-Time $700M Record As ‘Kingsman: The Golden Circle’ & ‘Lego Ninjago’ Enter Fall Fray|url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/kingsman-golden-circle-lego-ninjago-1202173819/|accessdate=2017-09-20|date=2017-09-20|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921015951/http://deadline.com/2017/09/kingsman-golden-circle-lego-ninjago-1202173819/|archive-date=2017-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房達2120萬美元，位居當週票房排名第三，該成績比前兩部《樂高》電影還低<ref name="opening" />。

